<placeName cert="high">Philadelphia</placeName></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>ὑπόμνημα Ζήνωνι παρὰ Ἀγάθωνος. περὶ ὧν σοι 

    <lb n="2"/>ἐμπεφάνικα, ἵνα κ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">α</unclear>ὶ κο<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">μ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ι</supplied>δήν τινα ποιήσηι, πρὸ <app type="editorial"><lem>τοῦ</lem><rdg>πι<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">σ</unclear>τοῦ</rdg></app> 

    <lb n="3"/>βασιλικὰ γενέσθαι· ὀφείλει γὰρ εἰς τὸ βασιλικὸν πολλά· 

    <lb n="4a"/>καὶ διδάξω ὅθεν τὴν κομιδὴν <choice><corr>ποιήσει</corr><sic>ποησει</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="4"/>καὶ περὶ ὧν σοι δύναμαι χρήσιμος γενέσθαι, ὥστε σε 

    <lb n="5"/>προσωφελεῖν <add place="supralinear">ἐκ τῆς γῆς</add> <del rend="erasure">εἰς τὸ βασιλικὸν</del> οὐκ ὀλίγον. εἰσὶν δὲ <expan><ex cert="high">ἄρουραι</ex></expan> <num value="265">σξε</num> 

    <lb n="6"/>ἃς <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">γε</supplied>ωργεῖ Πετοβάστις. ἀξιῶ οὖν παραδοθῆναί 

    <lb n="7"/>μοι ταύτας. ἐγὼ δέ σοι, ὅσην ἂν σιτοφορήσω ἀνα-

    <lb n="8"/>πληρώσω ἀκίνδυνον <expan>πυρ<ex cert="high">ῶν</ex></expan> <expan><ex cert="high">ἀρτάβας</ex></expan> <num value="10">ι</num>· εἰ δὲ μή, <num value="10">ι</num> <expan><ex cert="high">δραχμὰς</ex></expan> τὴν <expan><ex cert="high">ἄρουραν</ex></expan>. 

    <lb n="9"/>σὺ δὲ δύνηι ἐκ <num value="4">δ</num> <expan><ex cert="high">δραχμῶν</ex></expan> διαλύειν τὰ ἐκφόρια, ὥστε μηθὲν 

    <lb n="10"/>βλάπτεσθαί σε, ἀλλ᾽ ὠφελεῖσθαι <expan><ex cert="high">δραχμὰς</ex></expan> <num value="6">ϛ</num>. ἀναπαύσεις δὲ 

    <lb n="11"/>κατ᾽ ἐνιαυτὸν <expan><ex cert="high">ἄρουρας</ex></expan> <num value="100">ρ</num>, ἐγὼ δὲ ἀναπληρώσω τὴν <expan><ex cert="high">ἄρουραν</ex></expan> 

    <lb n="12"/>χόρτου <expan>δέ<ex cert="high">σμας</ex></expan> <choice><corr><expan><ex cert="high">δι</ex></expan>μν</corr><sic><app type="editorial"><lem>βμν</lem><rdg>β<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ι</unclear>ν</rdg></app></sic></choice><expan><ex cert="high">αίους</ex></expan> <num value="1500">Αφ</num>. καὶ <choice><corr>ἐὰν</corr><sic>εαμ</sic></choice> μὲν βούληι ἐκφόρια 

    <lb n="13"/>διαλύειν· εἰ δὲ μή, τιμῆς τὴν <expan><ex cert="high">ἄρουραν</ex></expan> <expan><ex cert="high">δραχμὰς</ex></expan> <num value="3">γ</num>. ὅσα δ᾽ ἂν 

    <lb n="14"/>χλωρὰ τὰ κτήνη ἐξανηλώσηι σου ἀνυπόλογόν σοι 

    <lb n="15"/>οἴσω, <add place="supralinear">σοῦ παρέχοντος τὸ σπέρμα</add> ὥστε καὶ τὰ κτήνη σου ἔχειν χορτάσματα 

    <lb n="16"/>δωρεάν. καὶ διδάξω σε ὅτι λύει. ὀψώνιον δέ μοι τά-

    <lb n="17"/>ξεις <choice><corr>σὺν</corr><sic>συμ</sic></choice> παντὶ κατὰ μῆνα <expan><ex cert="high">δραχμὰς</ex></expan> <num value="10">ι</num>. οὐ γὰρ προς 

    <lb n="18"/><gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/>επι<gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/> </ab></div><div n="meta.2083" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.2083" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="-226" notBefore="-275" type="textDate">Mitte III v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.2083" part="N" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Gehört zum Zenon - Archiv.</p></div><div n="meta.2083" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">PSI</title><biblScope type="volume">4</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">400</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">2083</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0238</series>; <biblScope type="volume">4</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">400</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0238;4;400" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.2083" part="N" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><listBibl><bibl type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">X</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">239</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">XI</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">244</biblScope></bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.2083" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p><bibl type="illustration">Pap.Flor. XXIV, Tav. XVII</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.2083" part="N" subtype="translations" type="bibliography"><head>Übersetzungen</head><listBibl lang="fr"><head lang="de">Französisch:</head><bibl type="translations">Orrieux, Les papyrus de Zenon (1983), S. 114</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.2083" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><placeName cert="high" type="ancientFindspot">Philadelphia</placeName> (